userdoc.notice: Node handles aggregating data pushed in from off-chain, and unlocks payment for oracles as they report. Oracles' submissions are gathered in rounds, with each round aggregating the submissions for each oracle into a single answer. The latest aggregated answer is exposed as well as historical answers and their updated at timestamp.
